quotes.healthQuoteText: Good health is not something we can buy. However, it can be an extremely valuable savings account. – Anne Wilson Schaef
quotes.helpPplQuoteText: At the end, it's not about what you have or even what you've accomplished. It's about who you've lifted up, who you've made better. It’s about what you've given back. – Denzel Washington

quotes.loveQuoteText: When we lose someone we love, we must learn not to live without them, but to live with the love they left behind. - Unknown
quotes.helpPplQuoteText: If you’re not making someone else’s life better, then you’re wasting your time. — Will Smith

quotes.loveQuoteText: There is a little boy inside the man who is my brother… Oh, how I hated that little boy. And how I love him too. — Anna Quindlen

quotes.healthQuoteText: Be bold, be brave enough to be your true self. - Queen Latifah
quotes.loveQuoteText: Because, if you could love someone, and keep loving them, without being loved back . . . then that love had to be real. It hurt too much to be anything else. ― Sarah Cross
quotes.helpPplQuoteText: No one is useless in this world who lightens the burdens of another. ― Charles Dickens
